dev.sl4sh.polarity.games

Interface GameBase

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractGame, SpleefGame

    public interface GameBase
    This interface is the base object for Polarity's games. No implementation is provided and it is recommended to inherit AbstractGame instead if you want to create a custom game
